{"tid":1301823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全力支持TVB商場活動","createTime":"2019-07-09T17:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T17:54:22.000Z","uid":220523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"63d43a6cd7360a244cc7ceff506e7edabe47b0f0","tid":1301823,"uid":220523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"作為香港一個大台，堅守新聞專業責無旁貸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱烈表揚</span></span>無綫電視喺反送中運動裏面嘅出色表現，<br />\n好想<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全力支持</span></span>所有TVB嘅商場活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為一個粉絲，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">舉牌、大叫口號</span></span>是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我初步諗到有幾樣好處：<br />\n1. 活動<span style=\"color: red;\">成本低</span>，我哋都係和平同熱愛大台，基本上佢冇可能隔絕曬熱心嘅支持者。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 係電視<span style=\"color: red;\">畫面</span>佢好難避開我哋精美嘅粉絲牌，而係<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收音</span></span>方面亦都好難避開我哋熱烈嘅支持口號。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 施壓俾所有廣告<span style=\"color: red;\">贊助活動</span>，如果活動取消亦都令<span style=\"color: red;\">藝人工作量</span>減少，可以得到寶貴嘅休息時間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次人唔使太多，有效果就得<br />\n我一個素人咩都唔識⋯⋯<br />\n大家覺得有冇得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係集中返火力係所有遊行同光復行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2e2d0979151d2e80a51faf23792055f96f5a40","tid":1301823,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\"